NYOVESTJohannesburg. &#8211; Cassper Nyovest has found the people responsible for vandalising his car. A distraught and angry Cassper took to Instagram last Thursday to tell fans that his car had been keyed outside a Johannesburg nightclub. He went on a massive manhunt and appealed to fans to help him find the culprits. And it seems that his search was a success.Taking to Twitter a few hours later Cassper tweeted that he had found the vandals &#8211; and what s worse it s people he knew.He did not reveal whether he had laid charges against the vandals. Cassper was naturally a bit upset after the incident but was soon in a better mood as he celebrated his birthday at Taboo nightclub in Johannesburg.The happy Mama I Made it star even gave fans a first real look at his growing Bentley collection. &#8211; Sowetan.